highlights.text: “Two High” by Moon Taxi is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 38 spots at #143.
“Mi Gente” by J Balvin and Willy William is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #32.
“That's What I Like” by Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 28 weeks straight.
Calvin Harris has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Feels (feat. Pharrell Williams, Katy Perry & Big Sean)” is the highest at #8.
